    <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2427.162228609594!2d105.73593738860906!3d21.053284178487992!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31345457e292d5bf%3A0x20ac91c94d74439a!2sHanoi%20University%20of%20Industry!5e1!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1713460368751!5m2!1sen!2s" 
